TITLE: Declaring Routes with Route Components in React Router
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates how to declare routes using Route components from React Router. It shows the basic structure for defining routes and their corresponding components, including examples of static and dynamic routes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/remix-run/react-router/blob/main/docs/start/declarative/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
