TITLE: Creating Search Route for Data Loading with Fetcher in React Router
DESCRIPTION: Sets up a search route with a loader function that filters users based on a query parameter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/remix-run/react-router/blob/main/docs/how-to/fetchers.md#2025-04-22_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
